---
title: Cheesy Beyond Meat®  Bolognese Ziti with Garlic
description: Feeling cheesy? This is the dinner for you! Penne Bolognese is finished in the oven with a hefty amount of mozza and Parm. But, the absolute best part about this veggie dinner, is it's cooked with only 2 pots!
